    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. Grid convergence, output comparison, and validation relevance results collectively support the claim that the CFD model can identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index criterion (RH < 1) is satisfied across all evaluated operating points. The assessment team accepts the model for the stated COU.",
